Track 11 Phase 4: Intervention Mutations

Implemented three teacher-facing SRS intervention mutations in convex/teacher/srs-mutations.ts:
- updateObjectivePriority: Changes objective policy (essential/triaged etc.) with teacher authorization
- resetStudentCards: Resets a student's SRS card to 'new' state and logs the reset action
- addExtraCards: Creates an additional new card for a student on a specific objective

All mutations validate teacher class ownership and student enrollment. Added comprehensive unit tests in __tests__/convex/teacher/srs-mutations.test.ts covering success paths, auth failures, and edge cases.
